& [OverlayLayerMap] is the refined landmark discipline
  + [reference_label_layer] is t-axis known-zero ordinates are named reference labels only
  + [sparse_landmark_layer] is vertical resonance candidates are metric-dependent finite extrema, with zeta_abs minima often nearer reference labels than Euler-product residual minima
